331
00:30:32,772 --> 00:30:38,214
along with our religious institutions, our sports teams, our political activities.

332
00:30:38,274 --> 00:30:52,137
These are essential components of our civic life, and the arts and humanities also are basically presenting opportunities for personal development and growth for every Medford citizen who takes part in them.

333
00:30:52,197 --> 00:30:56,399
So thanks again for this resolution.

