888
01:18:57,949 --> 01:18:59,970
As a matter of fact, Comcast has been voted

889
01:19:00,528 --> 01:19:08,435
the worst corporation in the country for customer services on the national agenda.

890
01:19:09,356 --> 01:19:26,292
