968
01:25:21,709 --> 01:25:23,370
So with that being said,

969
01:25:23,692 --> 01:25:28,434
You know, I just question whether or not, you know, this resolution's going to meet its purpose.

970
01:25:28,874 --> 01:25:31,775
I question whether or not we actually have the right to take the powers away from the executive.

971
01:25:31,795 --> 01:25:37,137
You know, we can ask that the mayor not do it, but to demand it or to require it, I don't think is within our scope.

972
01:25:37,357 --> 01:25:39,598
I think if you heard my question, it was respectfully request.

973
01:25:39,898 --> 01:25:40,658
That was the term.

974
01:25:41,078 --> 01:25:41,519
Very good.

